com.io7m.jtensors.core.unparameterized.matrices

Class Matrix4x4F.Builder

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.io7m.jtensors.core.unparameterized.matrices.Matrix4x4F.Builder
  • Enclosing class:
    Matrix4x4F

    public static final class Matrix4x4F.Builder
extends Object
    Builds instances of type Matrix4x4F. Initialize attributes and then invoke the build() method to create an immutable instance.

    Builder is not thread-safe and generally should not be stored in a field or collection, but instead used immediately to create instances.
